<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA061194-0071 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 050328 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 11, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
