<TEXT>
<P>
 Although "Doonesbury" creator Garry Trudeau refers to the Catholic church as 
blessing same-sex unions, most, but not all, of the claims of such unions point 
to rituals and practices of Catholics who later came to be identified with the 
Eastern Orthodox Church. Church spokesmen dispute the claims made in a book by 
Yale University professor John Boswell. 
