<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 11, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 4; Column 1; Advance Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
777 words 
</P>
