<TEXT>
<P>
 Former deputy chief -- A headline in Friday's Valley Edition inaccurately 
described misdemeanor charges filed against former Los Angeles Police 
Department Deputy Chief Daniel R. Sullivan. He was charged with illegally 
possessing confidential law enforcement information in the files of his private 
investigation company. 
</P>
